<p><strong>Aftermath:</strong> MTF Upsilon-53 were able to contact Administrative Site-10 and establish communication with the Foundation. They are the only known survivors of the incident. Area-R01 is currently considered lost, along with all staff therein. SCP-4011-1 have not yet made an attempt to breach the exterior of Area-R01.</p>
